                            <span class="bg-base-color mt-3 mx-auto mx-lg-0 sep-line-thick"></span>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-base">I met Andrew in college. Back then, I couldn’t even imagine he would become my fiance…We talked here and there and attended common classes sometimes. But everything changed during our last semester. One night, we went to have dinner together with a group of our friends, and, for the first time, Andrew sat next to me. We hit it off immediately, bonding over our mutual love for hiking and traveling. Three years later Andrew proposed. - Helen</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="carousel-cell align-items-center justify-content-center no-gutters row w-100">
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-5">
