                            <span class="d-block font-alt2 title-small">First "I Love You"</span>
                            <span class="bg-base-color mt-3 mx-auto mx-lg-0 sep-line-thick"></span>
                            <p class="mt-3 text-base">It was Valentine's day and Helen made us a romantic dinner with candles, hearts, and self-made cookies. I wanted to tell her those three words for a while, but couldn’t catch the right moment. I intended to tell her that night, but before I could she told something funny and made me laugh. I just said ‘Hahaha I love you’ totally organically. I was laughing really hard and those words just slipped out. Luckily, she felt the same way. Her face lit up and she told me "I love you too". - Andrew</p>
